Title: An Act Changing the Name of Agmalabo Elementary School in the Municipality of Ivisan, Province of Capiz, into Pang-Alaalang Paaralang Panfilo Mendoza
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 682
An Act Changing the Name of Agmalabo Elementary School in the Municipality of Ivisan, Province of Capiz, into Pang-Alaalang Paaralang Panfilo Mendoza
Section 1. The name of Agmalabo Elementary School in the Municipality of Ivisan, Province of Capiz, is changed to Pang-alaalang Paaralang Panfilo Mendoza.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
